In [3]:
@mylib.wrappers.wrapper_func_cache
def raw_data(previous_date, _universe, back_fill_length=20, vol_avg_length=120, filename=None, refresh=False, is_weight_sum=False):
    """利用 previous_date 交易日相关数据计算因子，供下一个交易日使用
    """
    trade_date = previous_date if isinstance(previous_date, list) else [previous_date]

    df_list = []
    uni = DynamicUniverse(_universe)
    
    for index, day in enumerate(trade_date):
        if (index + 1) % 60 == 0:
            print 'process No.{} day: {}'.format(index+1, day)
            
        secid = uni.preview(day, skip_halted=True)
        
        ### 因子信息
        df_factor = DataAPI.MktStockFactorsOneDayProGet(tradeDate=day.replace('-', ''), secID=secid, 
                                                        field=['secID', 'GSREV', 'ROEAvg', 'FixAssetRatio'])
        df_factor['tradeDate'] = day
        df_list.append(df_factor)
    
    df = pd.concat(df_list).reset_index(drop=True)
    
    return df
